<br>
You can always make up for lower level with good gear, to an extent.  Also, because the people that are L51, &amp; 52 will soon be levelling past the range they can kill the dragons, it seems fair to include them before a L43 that has a lot of opportunities to raid dragons yet ahead of them.  If you need more clerics, I see no reason why not to take a L44 cleric.  But if it's a choice between saying no to a L52 cleric, and taking a L43 instead, that seems wrong.  Nine levels is a LOT.  It's kinda like Venril Sathir.  You can take a L20 warrior if you want.  They just won't do much.  It's the rest of the crew that's 53+ that kills him.  Same with Nag Vox.  You can have a few people under 45, but it's the majority of the crew that's 47-52 that gets it done.<br>
<br>
Level is A LOT less critical now, due to server side filtering, but before it, it really mattered a lot, because you had a very limited number of people you could take on the raid.  If you brought too many people then, you'd lose people on the raid to LD.  As a result, it was very important to have everyone on the crew as high level &amp; as well equipped as possible.  That way, you can take fewer people, and run less risk of LD problems killing the raid. <p><img src="http://www.pangea.ca/~grinch/sadune.jpg" width="400" height="175"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukrungleeisenguss.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Krungle Eisenguss</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 114<br> <font color=#CC9900>(5/13/01 3:30:41 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/krungle101/krunglepic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What does the future hold: Nagafen/Vox</span><hr size=1> Adune, so lower the level and wiegh in Resist gear. Also, with your suggestion of Raid Leaders choosing some and Overseerers, or what ever you want to call them, choosing some, some lower levels will get in and the 50's will get in, too. I do have the gear and the armory. Being a Palli, at 41 our weapons skills are pretty much maxxed until post 50. Only thing that improves in that time is the gear and HP's. <br>
