<br>
While our skills don't increase past certain levels, your offensive and defensive abilities are tied to a formula that uses skill [and] level as variables.<br>
<br>
So essentially a level 10 (class) with a 55 1HB is still less likely to his than a level 55 with a 55 in 1HB.<br>
<br>
I'm using a very obvious difference in levels, but the factor still holds true at closer spreads in levels.<br>
<br>
As Hawkline pointed out, the same is also true of resists, your level also is a part of your resistances.<br>
<br>
Anyhow... turning back to Adun,<br>
<br>
When will we see this idea fleshed out and submitted for approval?<br>
